{"tid":1053773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[吸精神偷]日本警方拘兩漢　涉偷運和牛受精卵和精子到中國","createTime":"2019-03-09T10:26:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T11:33:03.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3f13bee27ede5514e6a6ab2fdcf065c20c2aae67","tid":1053773,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T10:26:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1446882-20190309.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1446882-20190309.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=i2Kzi6k%2Bo1XjTd2IKJX6ucRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=2e8cbc21\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1446882-20190309.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a331c529\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1446882-20190309.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n日本大阪警方拘捕兩名男子，涉嫌非法將和牛受精卵和精子走私到中國。<br />\n<br />\n52歲在大阪經營餐廳的男子，以及64歲無業男子，承認去年6月，未經檢疫部門許可，將和牛受精卵與精子帶往中國。<br />\n<br />\n農林水產省稱，受精卵和精子被裝在專門冷凍容器內，以渡輪運往中國，但被中國部門禁止入境，運回日本時被截獲。<br />\n<br />\n和牛在海外非常受歡迎，是日本主要的出口農產品之一，但目前未有法例防止受精卵及精子外流。若受精卵等外流並在海外生產，可能打擊日本畜牧業，鑑於案件當局上月開始探討對策。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u_g-YZh1j-w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Du_g-YZh1j-w&d=i2Kzi6k%2Bo1XjTd2IKJX6ucRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=d18d67d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u_g-YZh1j-w</a>"},{"pid":"a3ddec765ba1f3f1fa1d4379dbb1ad51866f9035","tid":1053773,"uid":33422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T10:30:21.000Z","msg":"又送豬瘟大禮，又偷和牛精子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />禮儀之邦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08a61041cba4bba0856e8b68b58317d65044dc22","tid":1053773,"uid":67280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T10:35:01.000Z","msg":"中國地理環境水清沙幼，養出黎既牛一定靚過小日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db77a0f19fa60bacdf7c2ac3d3ece48468981d33","tid":1053773,"uid":25676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T10:39:01.000Z","msg":"支畜天性真係男盜女娼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n地球毒瘤<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cee7ac38f207e39d7108ccecce5f24e00f754a62","tid":1053773,"uid":84585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T10:40:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b7643d140c69a72d8d5495dcf94330e9fadd78c","tid":1053773,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T10:45:43.000Z","msg":"支那狗 你認為你地支那水土 工作態度 可以培養出同日本和牛一樣嘅產品咩"},{"pid":"8491578e6261e67df0007d43073394cb8d8d00ef","tid":1053773,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cee7ac38f207e39d7108ccecce5f24e00f754a62","tid":1053773,"uid":84585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T10:40:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:31:51.000Z","msg":"另一單呀"},{"pid":"3e939b10c0340901536e4d211b31a2afd4bb9b36","tid":1053773,"uid":35233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:33:03.000Z","msg":"被中國部門禁止入境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}